{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013k5G8hR7Ch8K9q8ADW7qvi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the source file and convert it to a knowledge file JSON.\n\n**Step 1: Title**\nThe title is \"受信電文リーダ\" (from the first `=====` heading).\n\n**Step 1.5: Check for no-knowledge-content**\nThe source has Layer A and Layer B content - class names, property tables, configuration examples. So `no_knowledge_content: false`.\n\n**Step 2: Build section list**\nThe source has no h2 headings (no `-----` underlines). It's all one document under the main h1 title. Since there are no h2 sections, the entire content becomes one section: `s1`.\n \n**Step 3: Extract content**\n\nNow I'm pulling out the key technical details: the `MessageReader` class and `ReceivedMessage` data type, along with their properties and behavior. The Layer A content describes how `hasNext()` always returns true unless explicitly closed, returns null on timeout or when closed, and blocks when the queue is empty.\n\nWhen an error occurs, it throws an error response message object as a runtime exception. Layer B mirrors the same class structure with properties and code examples.\n\n**Step 4: Cross-references**\n\nNo special documentation references like `:java:extdoc:`, `:ref:`, or `:doc:` appear in the source.\n\n**Step 5: Hints**\n\nI'm noting the key terms and class names to track: `MessageReader`, the full package path `nablarch.fw.messaging.reader.MessageReader`, `ReceivedMessage`, and the property names like `receiveQueueName`, `readTimeout`, `formatFileName`, and `formatFileDirName`.\n\n**Step 6: official_doc_urls**\n\nSince the base URL is empty, I'll set `official_doc_urls` to an empty array with no Javadoc URLs to include.\n\nNow I'm composing the section for the message reader, starting with the class name `nablarch.fw.messaging.reader.MessageReader` and describing how it handles incoming messages from a queue—blocking until a message arrives or times out, then returning null if the timeout is reached or the reader is closed.\n\nGenerating properties table... Writing XML configuration...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21213,"cache_read_input_tokens":29955,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":21213,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01ab3929-db08-4e22-a276-de0d21aa668a","uuid":"febfbb82-744a-4af4-b13f-d692b7810005"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013k5G8hR7Ch8K9q8ADW7qvi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Ka53zzvMbe3qrdenf9i6DX","name":"StructuredOutput","input":{"id":"readers-MessageReader","title":"受信電文リーダ","no_knowledge_content":false,"official_doc_urls":[],"index":[{"id":"s1","title":"受信電文リーダ","hints":["MessageReader","nablarch.fw.messaging.reader.MessageReader","ReceivedMessage","nablarch.fw.messaging.ReceivedMessage","receiveQueueName","readTimeout","formatFileName","formatFileDirName","受信電文リーダ","メッセージキュー監視","受信待機タイムアウト","DIリポジトリ登録"]}],"sections":{"s1":"**クラス名**: `nablarch.fw.messaging.reader.MessageReader`\n\n**読み込むデータの型**: `nablarch.fw.messaging.ReceivedMessage`\n\n`read()` 呼び出し時、監視対象キューの受信電文を待機する。キューが空の場合は電文受信またはタイムアウト時間経過までブロックする。タイムアウトまたはリーダが閉じられている場合は `null` を返す。\n\n> **重要**: `hasNext()` は常に `true` を返す。明示的に `close()` を呼び出さない限り終端しない。\n\n受信電文読み込み時にエラーが発生した場合は、エラー応答電文オブジェクトを実行時例外として送出する。\n\n| プロパティ名 | 型 | 必須 | デフォルト値 | 説明 |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| receiveQueueName | String | ○ | | 受信キュー論理名 |\n| readTimeout | long | | 5000 | 受信待機タイムアウト時間(ミリ秒)。0以下を設定した場合はメッセージ受信まで待機し続ける |\n| formatFileName | String | | | 受信メッセージのフォーマット定義ファイル名（デフォルトフォーマットを設定したい場合のみ使用） |\n| formatFileDirName | String | | | 受信メッセージのフォーマット定義ファイルディレクトリ論理名 |\n\nJava例:\n```java\nlong readTimeout = 15 * 1000; // 15sec\n\nDataReader<ReceivedMessage> reader = new MessageReader()\n                                    .setReceiveQueueName(\"LOCAL.RECEIVE\")\n                                    .setReadTimeout(readTimeout);\n```\n\nXML例:\n```xml\n<component\n  class = \"nablarch.fw.messaging.reader.MessageReader\"\n  name  = \"dataReader\">\n  <property\n    name  = \"receiveQueueName\"\n    value = \"LOCAL.RECEIVE\"\n  />\n  <property\n    name  = \"readTimeout\"\n    value = \"${readTimeout}\"\n  />\n</component>\n```"}}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21213,"cache_read_input_tokens":29955,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":21213,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01ab3929-db08-4e22-a276-de0d21aa668a","uuid":"bc809ef6-5b68-42c9-8578-4b52f271d113"}
